views.text: Our physician uses a fine instrument, less than one millimeter in diameter, to harvest individual follicular units from your scalp. This tool creates a small circular incision around each unit, allowing for precise graft isolation. The grafts are then extracted with a tweezer-like instrument and meticulously prepared by our team of expert technicians. They ensure each follicular unit, containing 1-4 hairs, is in prime condition for transplantation. The strategic placement of these units by our Dream physicians is what delivers natural-looking results and showcases our artistic excellence.

views.text: Leveraging the precision of FUE harvesting techniques, our robotic system ensures meticulous follicular unit extraction without the fatigue that can affect human performance. views.text: The Follicular Unit Strip Surgery (FUSS) technique involves extracting a strip of tissue from the back of the head, which serves as a rich source of donor hair follicles. Our expert team meticulously harvests the follicles from this strip, preparing them for individual transplantation. FUSS is often the method of choice for advanced hair loss, as it maximizes the use of the scalp area to meet patient expectations. This method generally allows for the largest number of grafts to be transplanted in one session, making it highly efficient.
views.desc: <button bound_box=87,1413,993,1416>The Follicular Unit Strip Surgery (FUSS) technique</button>

views.text: Our clinic offers the best of both worlds with our hybrid hair transplant surgery. This innovative approach combines the high-volume graft benefits of FUSS and the precision and naturalness of FUE. By integrating these methods, we can maximize density, coverage, and the overall aesthetic of the transplanted area for superior results.

views.text: Dream Hairline stands out by dedicating our practice exclusively to hair transplants. We tailor each procedure to the unique pattern of baldness and symptoms of our patients, ensuring the precise number of grafts are used without waste. Our clinic is proud to offer the innovative hybrid surgery approach, combining FUSS for a high quantity of grafts with FUE for additional grafts to enhance naturalness, density, and coverage in thinning areas. The legacy of innovation began in 1985 with Dr. Choi's invention of the Choi Implanter, the original pen-like transplanter. In 2007, Dr. Choi and Dr. Park, the innovators behind the KNP suture technique, co-founded DreamHairLine. With doctors boasting over a decade of experience, we are fully equipped to deliver the exceptional results you seek.
views.desc: <button bound_box=30,1413,1050,1416>Dream Hairline stands out by dedicating our practi</button>

views.text: We proudly offer the ARTAS Robot FUE, the latest and most advanced hair transplant technology. Our services include non-shaven and fully shaven FUE, where follicular units are manually extracted, as well as FUSS (single strip harvesting). The choice of surgical method is customized based on the client's hair loss condition, hair type, including thickness and density, and the scalp's elasticity or rigidity.
